 time to answer my question. These posts have some great information. I look forward to trying the various methods and seeing which works best.<br><br>Thanks again<br>-Traxxus<br>More Informed Ranger of Surefall <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usteeltoefv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SteeltoeFV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/6/02 10:10:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1286.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What's the best way to devide loot?</span><hr size=1> The easiest method for distibuting loot is 'Need before Greed'. <p><B>Steeltoe</B><i> Guardian of Kaladim and Slayer of Ogres</I><BR>Level 13 Dwarven Warrior<BR><BR><B>Steelfaith</B><I> Acolyte of the Holy Brell</I><BR>Level 12 Dwarven Cleric<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usliver123.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sliver123</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 51<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/6/02 11:22:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1286.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What's the best way to devide loot?</span><hr size=1> This server seems to have an inherently NBG attitude from my experience, due to the youth of the server and the fact that there are no or few opportunities to twink. Tempers greed somewhat. I have seen people try to exploit NBG when they are the right class but have NO intention of using an item. I've seen warriors with lamentations try to call NBG on a lamentation drop <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Was an eyebrow raiser if ever i saw one. <br>Also seen someone NBG a fungi tunic, and five minutes later auction to the zone, WTS fungi tunic. <br>Be aware of these gimps <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ufeneant.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Feneant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 297<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/6/02 12:30:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1286.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What's the best way to devide loot?</span><hr size=1> In groups im with, loot is always master looting with need before greed and whatever else that's worthwhile gets rolled on.<br><br>I've only had problems with a person once who rolled on something we knew he wouldn't use (he had said so himself then changed his story) and have not grouped with him or his guild since (2 months of that) and have not run in any problems since then.  When I was lower, groups were FFA but you always had at least 1 in the group who looted a lot more than the rest and the casters were left out so we stopped. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=1286.topic&start=21&stop=32>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=1286.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionavief